**On your own computer**
To install mpi4py with Anaconda:
    conda install mpi4py
To run:
    mpiexec -np (number of processes) python (filename).py
    
**On Blue Waters**
To enable mpi4py on Blue Waters:
    module load bwpy
    module load bwpy-mpi
To run:
    aprun -n (number of processes) python (filename).py

Examples copied with permission from Dr. Brian W O'Shea at Michigan State Univ
